snippet.title: Tauba Tauba | Bad Newz | Vicky Kaushal | Triptii Dimri | Karan Aujla | In cinemas 19th July
snippet.description:
Experience the magic of Karan Aujla, Triptii Dimri and Vicky Kaushal's first-ever collaboration in "Tauba Tauba" from Bad Newz! This high-energy dance number is guaranteed to make you move. Get ready to dance like never before!

üëâ Subscribe to Saregama Music: https://bit.ly/3FkAS0W

Credits:
Composer - Karan Aujla
Singer - Karan Aujla
Lyricist - Karan Aujla
Music Producer - Yeah Proof
Special Thanks Azeem Dayani
Mixing And Mastering - Hanish Taneja
Choreographer - Bosco- Ceaser
Song Editor- Adele Jerome Pereira
Production Designer- Manini Mishra
DOP- Santhana Krishnan Ravichandran
Costume Designer- Samidha Wangnoo

Bad Newz in cinemas 19th July.

Amazon Prime presents
In association with Dharma Productions and Leo Media Collective
A Leo Media Collective production
BAD NEWZ
Starring Vicky Kaushal, Triptii Dimri and Ammy Virk
Directed by Anand Tiwari
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Apoorva Mehta, Amritpal Singh Bindra & Anand Tiwari
Written by Ishita Moitra & Tarun Dudeja

Lyrics:

Husn tera tauba tauba X 4
Oh le liya ladki ne dil humara,
Abhi thoda saaf nahi lag raha irada,
Choti bahaut lambi nahi rakhi hai mutiyar ne,
Haaye dikhta nahi hai parranda, dikhta hai Prada,
Figure se lagti Latino
Ek baar batado itni kyun ho shaukinon,
Kal hi tum Italy se aayi hai marjaaniye, aur purse tenu Paris se mangvaya hai Valentino
Haan tujhe kyun na dekhu, tujhse kya seekhu, tujh mein kya likhu?

Husn tera tauba tauba X 4

Hum hai malana aur who kief,
Aira-gaira dekhti nahi waise toh shareef hoon, yahaan par kehti hai too much desi hai,
isliye chill kare London aur party at Ibiza hai, humaare liye bilkul bhee free nahi lagti, IG
story pe toh Bora Bora , awaaz tumhari sohniye surilee noori ke (Old Punjabi singer) jaise
lagti, jab kamar hile ‚ÄúNora‚Äù lagti,
Milna dass de (bata de), tha (jagah) dass de, meri jaan dass de (bata de),

Husn tera tauba tauba X 4

Haaye! Mitron se aankh tumhari maange kangna (mujhse tumhari aankh Kangana maang
rahi hai),
Abhi main banwa dunga mujhe bata toh sahi,
Jaan maang lo main tujhpe jaan waar (jaan nyochavar karna) du, khud nikal jaayegi tu
hass toh sahi, tujhmein nasha pehli tod (daaru) jaisa hai kude (girl), sohniye daru ka toh
naam lagta hai, hum se zyaada tumhari popularity ho gayi hai, tum bahar nikli toh sadko
par jam (traffic jam) lagta hai,
Haa... baat maan meri, mehman meri, tum ho jaan meri,

Husn tera tauba tauba X 4

Figure se lagti Latino

story pe toh Bora Bora , awaaz tumhari sohniye surilee noori ke (Old Punjabi singer) jaise
lagti, jab kamar hile ‚ÄúNora‚Äù lagti,

hass toh sahi, tujhmein nasha pehli tod (daaru) jaisa hai kude (girl), sohniye daru ka toh
naam lagta hai, hum se zyaada tumhari popularity ho gayi hai, tum bahar nikli toh sadko

snippet.title: Bajaj Freedom CNG Bike - Kya Sahi, Kya Nahi | First Look
snippet.description: Bajaj CNG motorcycle - Freedom 125 - has finally gone on sale in India at a starting price of Rs 95,000 whereas the top-end Disc brake + LED light version costs Rs 1.10 lacs (ex-showroom). What makes it unique is the fact that it gets a 2KG CNG tank beneath the seat and a 2-litre petrol fuel tank. cumulatively, both offer a range of 330Km (realistic range). On CNG alone, it offers over 108kmpl thus making it the most fuel efficient motorcycle on sale in India right now. Hope you enjoy this video.

A notable tag-team effort which is exemplified by its raw, authentic feel and the gritty aesthetic of their music, ‚ÄúKODAK‚Äù is a rare sight to behold for one and all.

snippet.title: From PM Modi To Manipur MP, Here Are The Most Controversial Speeches Of the 18th Lok Sabha
snippet.description:
Parliament Speech: As the 18th Lok Sabha session concludes, we revisit some of the most controversial speeches made by prominent leaders. From Prime Minister Modi's striking remarks to Rahul Gandhi's fiery rebuttals, and Mahua Moitra's bold statements to Anurag Thakur's vehement arguments, each speech left a significant mark on the parliamentary proceedings. The sessions also featured impassioned speeches by Bimol Akoijam on regional issues, Asaduddin Owaisi's critiques of government policies, and Harsimrat Kaur Badal's pointed accusations. This compilation captures the intensity and drama that defined this session.

snippet.title: Team India meets Prime Minister Narendra Modi
snippet.description:
The T20 World Cup-winning Indian cricket team landed in Delhi on July 4 aboard a specially-arranged charter flight, five days after winning the coveted title in Barbados where it was stranded due to a category 4 hurricane.

The team met Prime Minister Narendra Modi before leaving for Mumbai where a victory parade is scheduled for the T20 World Cup champions at 5 p.m.

The Indian team will be celebrating the win at The Wankhede Stadium in mumbai later today. The stadium will be open to general public as well.

The gates will close at 6 p.m. or when the stands are filled to capacity, whichever is earlier.

For live updates on Team India arrival click here: https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/team-india-arrival-live-updates-july-4/article68365597.ece

snippet.title: Mahua Moitra Returns To Lok Sabha With Fiery Speech, Corners Modi Govt On Manipur, Kashmir & Ayodhya
snippet.description:
TMC Lok Sabha MP Mahua Moitra made her comeback speech while replying to the motion of thanks to the President's address. Notably, the TMC MP was suspended from Lok Sabha just months from elections over cash-for-query allegations. Mahua denied any wrongdoing. And in her comeback speech, she came down heavily on BJP and the Modi government. In her more than half-an-hour-long speech, Mahua cornered BJP over Manipur violence, Kashmir, Ayodhya and many more issues.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
Welcome to the GRAND FINALS of the BGIS 2024

Feel the pulse-pounding intensity as the top 16 teams converge on the battleground for a shot at ultimate glory in BGIS history. This is more than just a tournament round, it's the climax of the BATTLEGROUNDS MOBILE INDIA SERIES 2024, where dreams soar and legends are made. With a massive prize pool of INR 2 Crores, the stakes are at their peak.

16 Lan Finalists: GLOBAL ESPORTS, TEAM AARU, X SPARK, iQOO SOUL, FS ESPORTS, VASISTA ESPORTS, TEAM TAMILAS, R4VEN ESPORTS, CARNIVAL GAMING, MOGO ESPORTS, TEAM LIMRA, VENOM GAMING, 8 BIT, TEAM INSANE ESPORTS, INFERNO SQUAD, RECKONING ESPORTS.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Welcome to our Tamil Devotional Channel, your ultimate destination for soulful and uplifting Tamil devotional songs. Dive into the divine with our carefully curated collections designed to inspire and bring peace to your soul every day of the week.

Daily Devotional Songs:

* Muruga Tamil Devotional Songs: Invoke the valor and blessings of Lord Muruga.
* Hanuman Tamil Devotional Songs: Feel the strength and devotion of Lord Hanuman.
* Amman Tamil Devotional Songs: Honor the divine mother in her various forms.
* Saibaba Tamil Devotional Songs: Seek the blessings of Shirdi Sai Baba.

* Devi Tamil Devotional Songs: Praise the supreme goddess Devi in her many avatars.
* Ganesh Tamil Devotional Songs: Start your day with prayers to Lord Ganesha.

Special Occasions and Deities:
* Amavasai Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs for the new moon day rituals.
* Pradosham Tamil Devotional Songs: Hymns for the auspicious Pradosham period.
* Ashta Lakshmi Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs dedicated to the eight forms of Goddess Lakshmi.

* Surya Tamil Devotional Songs: Worship the Sun God, Surya, with these melodies.

* Guru Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs to honor Guru and seek his wisdom.
* Perumal Tamil Devotional Songs: Devote to Lord Perumal with these spiritual songs.
* Navagraha Tamil Devotional Songs: Balance your energies with songs for the nine planets.

snippet.title: Mirzapur Season 3 REVIEW | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
Mirzapur Season 3 Review By Deeksha Sharma. Mirzapur Season 3 Streaming on Amazon Prime Featuring Pankaj Tripathi, Ali Fazal, Shweta Tripathi, Rasika Dugal is the Biggest OTT Show comeback after 4 years with Munna Bhaiya vs Guddu Bhaiya vs Kaleen Bhaiya 3 way race to Power reaching to its conclusion. Mirzapur 3 is back with Suspense Twist & Mind bending Climax with Surprise New characters challenging the old masters for the Ultimate Throne. Mirzapur 3 Full Web Series Story Outline Explained & Positives Negatives would be shared in this Video. Mirzapur 3 - The Biggest Indian Web Series ever or Kalki 2898 AD Prabhas Movie will steal all the headlines? Do leave your Public Review in the Comments below.

Mirzapur Ki Nayi ABCD! ft. Pankaj Tripathi, Ali Fazal, Divyenndu | Prime Video India

As we all wait for the new season of Mirzapur, here is a quick replay to refresh your memory until we see who Mirzapur's new king! Watch it now, only on Prime Video India!

About:
The iron-fisted Akhandanand Tripathi is a millionaire carpet exporter and the mafia don of Mirzapur. His son, Munna, is an unworthy, power hungry heir who will stop at nothing to inherit his father‚Äôs legacy. An incident at a wedding procession forces him to cross paths with Ramakant Pandit, an upstanding lawyer, and his sons, Guddu and Bablu.

Prime Video India Presents
Mirzapur Season 3 Official Trailer
Starring Pankaj Tripathi, Ali Fazal, Shweta Tripathi Sharma, Rasika Dugal, Vijay Varma, Isha Talwar, Anjumm Shharma, Priyanshu Painyuli, Harshita Shekhar Gaur, Rajesh Tailang, Sheeba Chadha, Pramod Pathak, Shernavaz Jijina, Meghna Malik, Manu Rishi Chadha, Neha Sargam, Liliput Faroqui, Alka Amin, Anangsha Biswas, Shahnawaz Pradhan, Rohit Tiwari, Prashansa Sharma, Anil George
Directed by Gurmmeet Singh and Anand Iyer
Produced by Excel Media & Entertainment
Written by Apurva Dhar Badgaiyan, Avinash Singh Tomar, Avinash Singh and Vijay Narayan Verma

Official Release Date July 5, 2024 on Prime Video India.

snippet.title: 'Manipur Burning, Govt a Mute Spectator For a Year': What Opposition Said on Manipur in Parliament
snippet.description:
Several opposition leaders, in the motion of thanks on the President's Address in Lok Sabha, slammed the government over Manipur Violence. Inner Manipur MP from Congress party, Angomcha Bimol Akoijam said the government had been a "mute spectator" on the Manipur violence for over a year. Leader of Opposition, Rahul Gandhi asked the PM why he hasn't visited Manipur ever since the violence started there in May 2023. TMC MP Mahua Moitra also slammed the government for not stopping the violence in a "burning Manipur".
#manipur #parliament #manipurviolence #loksabha

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Habil Aur Qabil Episode 26 - [Eng Sub] - Aagha Ali - Yashma Gill - Asad Siddiqui - Nawal Saeed - 4th July 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Haris, a young and handsome perfectionist, excels in every aspect of life, often overshadowing his younger brother Qadir, who is dull and simple. Despite Qadir's sacrifices for his brother's happiness, Haris always gets his way.

Meanwhile, Sobia, a clever but impoverished relative of Haris and Qadir, manipulates Qadir into falling in love with her, leading to their impending marriage. As Haris struggles with his romantic pursuits, facing obstacles with his love, Hooram, jealousy drives him to abandon Hooram and
pursue Sobia. This decision sparks tension between the brothers, exacerbated when Sobia exploits the situation to her advantage.

Will Haris end up with Sobia? Will Qadir stand up against his brother? Will Hooram discover the real reason why Haris left her? Will Sobia choose Haris over Qadir? Will Qadir forever live in Haris's shadow?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

Writer: Zanjabeel Asim

Mahmood Aslam as Qasim

snippet.title: Keerai Thokku Recipe in Tamil | Spinach Gravy Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make keerai thokku recipe in tamil. This is a healthy recipe which is very tasty and the main star of the dish is fresh green spinach leaves. We have to make sure that the spinach is cooked just right and not too much that they brown and wither. This side dish can be served along with white rice and can also be served as a side dish for chapathi / dosa or idli.
#keeraithokku #keerairecipe #keeraikootu 

Friends, please do try this spinach gravy at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!


Ingredients for Keerai Thokku:
For grinding:
1 tsp Oil
1 tbsp Channa dal
1 tbsp Coriander seeds
1 tsp Cumin seeds
1 tsp Oil
1 Onion
6-7 Garlic cloves
1/5 tsp Chilli powder
1/2 Tomato
1 small piece Tamarind

1 tbsp Oil
1/4 tsp Mustard seeds
4-5 fenugreek
4-5 garlic cloves
2 red chilli
Curry leaves
250g spinch
required Salt
1-2 tbsp Oil extra
